{
  "id": "adv_event_2604_02_01",
  "title": "こんにちは！ブリスケ！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "ナレーション",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "とある休日。雫、怜、さくら、千紗は遙子に夕飯用の\n魚の調達を命じられ、星見市の海で釣りをしていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.3333333015,
      "endTime": 16.05206213,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2333.3333651999997
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2333.3333651999997
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4433.3333652
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5533.3333652
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～、どうしよう。お魚さん、全然釣れないね……\nこのままだと今夜の夕飯は食べるものがないよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6333326657,
      "endTime": 30.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "さ～く～ら～？　魚を買うお金を全部『魚魚っとさん\nガチャガチャ』につぎ込んだのは誰だったかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.63333203,
      "endTime": 40.8236270586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "だ、だって……どうしても『黄金爆レア魚魚っとさん』\nが欲しかったんだもん！　すぐ出ると思ったんだもん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.0333322842,
      "endTime": 51.3193638164,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも喧嘩しないで～！　途中で怜ちゃんもヤケに\nなってさくらちゃんと一緒にガチャガチャしてたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.5333322842,
      "endTime": 60.1513140042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "それは……十回も回して出ないなんて悔しいじゃない\nここまで来たら出るまで回さなきゃ負けっていうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3666656176,
      "endTime": 69.60759503039999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "そう！　その通りだよ！　優ちゃんも言ってたよ！\n出るまで回せば実質タダ……推しが出れば勝ちやねん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7999989509,
      "endTime": 79.39830160140001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "それは違うよ、さくらちゃん。タダじゃなかったでしょ\n夕飯のお魚を買うお金と引き換えに、手に入れたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.2666662852,
      "endTime": 88.5869398435,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9533.334700300004
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12266.668828400001
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14166.668828399992
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-02.m4a",
          "delay": 15900.002161700002
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_fishing-03.m4a",
          "delay": 9533.334700300004
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12533.335495099991
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14700.002161699998
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-02.m4a",
          "delay": 16533.33549509999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "みんなー……ヘルプ！　こっちに来て……！\n一人じゃ釣り上げられない、大物の予感！　わくわく！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.8000009855,
      "endTime": 96.38000119530001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "大変！　雫が海の中に引きずり込まれそうだわ！\nみんなで助けに行くわよ！　雫ーーーーっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.5666676522,
      "endTime": 105.040935421,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-02.m4a",
          "delay": 533.3341281000088
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4633.334128100003
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6600.000794700009
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1366.6674613999987
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3366.6674613999985
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2433.3341281000003
