    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "buriburi",
      "speakerName": "魚",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-buriburi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-buriburi001.m4a",
      "text": "ビチビチビチビチビチビチ～～～～～ッ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.3333373708,
      "endTime": 126.9800046605,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2333.3338419
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1166.6626292000046
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-03.m4a",
          "delay": 3833.3338419
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "やったー！　釣れた！　むむむ……フォルムが\nなんとなーく魚魚っとさんに似てる気もするけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.1666712127,
      "endTime": 138.892861589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "魚魚っとさん……ではないよね？　んん……？\nねえ、怜ちゃん、このお魚さんはもしかして……チラッ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.1000045461,
      "endTime": 150.4907638235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "ブ……リ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.7000157359,
      "endTime": 153.3000156405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-buriburi002.m4a",
      "text": "違う、ブリは80cmから。この子は79cmだから\nまだ『ワラサ』。とりあえず脳締めで動きを止め――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.4666874889,
      "endTime": 160.5438755039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "buriburi",
      "speakerName": "魚",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-buriburi.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ッ！？　お願いだブリ！　まだオラを食べないでブリ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.6000198051,
      "endTime": 164.96667900100002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "buriburi",
      "speakerName": "魚",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-buriburi.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あともう少しでオラは完璧なブリになれるブリ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.966679001,
      "endTime": 169.7466823264,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "魚が喋った！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.9333490693,
      "endTime": 172.3607640111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "うひょ～っ！　星見大五郎界隈で噂されていたこの限定\nロッドで釣った魚は人語を喋るって本当だったんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.5666824027,
      "endTime": 181.991711013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "buriburi",
      "speakerName": "ブリ山ブリスケ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-buriburi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2604_02_01-buriburi003.m4a",
      "text": "ブリブリブリッ。オラの名前はブリ山ブリスケ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.2000106498,
      "endTime": 190.0543855354,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "buriburi",
      "speakerName": "ブリ山ブリスケ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
